(8, 'Olivier G Balzac', NULL, '82945564227', NULL, 'Good day, \r\n \r\nMy name is Olivier G Balzac. I previously sent you a letter regarding a transaction involving 13.5 million US dollars, which was left by my deceased client. As I have not received a response from you, I have chosen to reach out again through this platform. After reviewing your profile, I am firmly convinced that you are capable of managing this transaction alongside me very effectively. \r\n \r\nI would like to highlight that upon the successful completion of the transaction, 10% of the funds will be donated to charitable organizations, while the remaining 90% will be divided between us, resulting in an equal distribution of 45% each. \r\n \r\nPlease respond at your earliest convenience to obtain further details about the transaction. \r\n \r\nSincerely, \r\n \r\nOlivier G Balzac, \r\nAttorney. \r\nE-mail: info@balzacavocate.com \r\nWebsite: http://www.balzacavocate.com/', NULL, '2026-06-11 07:09:34', '2026-06-11 07:09:34'),
(9, 'DavidAnatt', NULL, '82234454977', NULL, 'Good day! assessmentbd.com, \r\nI found assessmentbd.com while checking different websites. \r\nWe offer automated contact form messaging for marketing. \r\nMany companies use similar platforms to expand their online communication. \r\nPricing for the platform is structured to remain accessible. \r\nA free demo is available so you can see how the platform works. \r\nYou are welcome to contact us if this could be relevant for you. \r\n \r\nAppreciate your time. \r\nContact us. \r\nTelegram - https://t.me/FeedbackFormEU \r\nWhatsApp - +375259112693 \r\nWhatsApp  https://wa.me/+375259112693', NULL, '2026-06-11 08:32:23', '2026-06-11 08:32:23');
