(91, 'Digital Marketing For Freelancing Level 3', 'Level 3', 'Information And Communication Technology', 'Information And Communication Technology', 'Digital Marketing For Freelancing', 'digital-marketing-for-freelancing-level-3', 'Embark on a transformative journey with our Digital Marketing For Freelancing Level 3 course, designed to equip you with advanced skills to thrive in the competitive freelance market. You\'ll delve into sophisticated digital marketing strategies, including advanced SEO techniques, paid advertising campaigns (PPC), social media marketing mastery, content strategy development, email marketing automation, and analytics interpretation. This course focuses on practical application, ensuring you gain hands-on experience with industry-standard digital marketing tools and platforms essential for a successful freelance career.\r\n\r\nThis comprehensive curriculum is meticulously aligned with NSDA standards, specifically preparing you to confidently ace the NSDA Digital Marketing Level 3 certification exam. We integrate targeted modules that focus on understanding the exam structure, practicing with relevant NSDA written questions, and mastering various MCQ question formats. Our training emphasizes the competencies required for CBT&A (Competency-Based Training & Assessment), ensuring you not only gain theoretical knowledge but also develop the practical skills necessary to demonstrate your expertise effectively and pass your NSDA assessment with flying colors.\r\n\r\nUpon completion, you\'ll be ready to secure high-paying freelance projects, build your client portfolio, and establish yourself as a sought-after digital marketing professional. AssessmentBD provides the expert guidance and resources needed to transform your aspirations into a certified, successful freelance career.', 'Master Digital Marketing L3: Freelance Success & NSDA Pass', 'Launch your thriving freelance career with Digital Marketing L3! Master essential tools, conquer NSDA written questions & MCQs, and excel in CBT&A assessments. Enroll today!', 'digital marketing course, freelancing digital marketing, level 3 digital marketing, NSDA exam questions, CBT&A assessment, marketing tools for freelancers, NSDA written questions, MCQ questions digital marketing, digital marketing certification, freelance marketing strategies', NULL, 1, 0, NULL, 91, '2026-05-20 02:44:11', '2026-05-27 07:03:18'),
