trical System Installation And Maintenance Level 1<\\/p>\\n    <\\/td>\\n  <\\/tr>\\n\\n  <tr>\\n    <td style=\\\"padding:36px 40px;\\\">\\n      \\n            <p style=\'font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 12px\'>\\n                অভিনন্দন, MD. MAZHARUL HOQUE! 🎊\\n            <\\/p>\\n            <p style=\'color:#475569;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 16px\'>\\n                আপনার subscription সফলভাবে approve করা হয়েছে। এখন আপনি সব exam ও study materials access করতে পারবেন।\\n            <\\/p>\\n            <div style=\'background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:0 0 20px\'>\\n                <p style=\'margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#15803d;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em\'>Subscription Details<\\/p>\\n                <table style=\'width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;\'>\\n                    <tr><td style=\'padding:6px 0;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;width:120px;font-weight:600;\'>কোর্স<\\/td><td style=\'padding:6px 0;color:#0f172a;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;\'>Solar Electrical System Installation And Maintenance Level 1<\\/td><\\/tr>\\n                    <tr><td style=\'padding:6px 0;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;\'>Plan<\\/td><td style=\'padding:6px 0;color:#0f172a;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;\'>Basic<\\/td><\\/tr>\\n                    <tr><td style=\'padding:6px 0;color:#64748b;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;\'>মেয়াদ<\\/td><td style=\'padding:6px 0;color:#0f172a;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;\'>10 Jul 2026 পর্যন্ত<\\/td><\\/tr>\\n                <\\/table>\\n            <\\/div>\\n            <div style=\'text-align:center;margin:24px 0\'>\\n            <a href=\'https:\\/\\/assessmentbd.com\\/dashboard\' style=\'display:inline-block;background:#0b57d0;color:#fff;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:12px;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-.01em;\'>\\n                এখনই শুরু করুন →\\n           